Modify field documentation to support custom help via the "help" keyword.

Note the "help=" that is followed by an object field (ie Database field)
help information. This is useful when you want to have a user definable
help message associated with a particular database field.

Ex:
<a class="cluetip" href="#" rel="index.php?module=documentation&amp;view=view&amp;help={$cflg.field_help}"
   title="{$LANG.custom_flags_upper}"><img src="{$help_image_path}help-small.png" alt="" /></a>
